        "setup": "For Weaviate Cloud, open the [Weaviate Cloud console](https://console.weaviate.cloud), create or select your cluster, and copy the **Administrator API Key** plus the **REST Endpoint URL** from the cluster connection details as shown in the [quickstart](https://docs.weaviate.io/weaviate/quickstart). For self-hosted Weaviate with RBAC/user management, create a database user and API key via the [user management API](https://docs.weaviate.io/weaviate/configuration/rbac/manage-users) or preconfigure keys in deployment settings as described in the [authentication guide](https://docs.weaviate.io/deploy/configuration/authentication).",
